  "issue_number": 8857,
  "issue_title": "xds: build the interceptor chain for routes with cluster_specifier_plugins as well",
  "issue_body": "We are currently building the interceptor chain only for routes that point to weighted_clusters. See: https://github.com/grpc/grpc-go/blob/c7ec4d9ae3281bc57a8adce59b572e56965fb728/internal/xds/resolver/xds_resolver.go#L374\n\nAnd not doing so in the case where the route points to a cluster_specifier_plugin. See: https://github.com/grpc/grpc-go/blob/c7ec4d9ae3281bc57a8adce59b572e56965fb728/internal/xds/resolver/xds_resolver.go#L365\n\nThis needs to be fixed. Interceptor chain needs to be build for all cluster types. As part of this change, we also need to add a test to ensure that filters work properly for routes that match to cluster_specifier_plugins.",
  "merged_at": "2026-05-20T05:49:43Z",
